Rachel True https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rachel_True 0 Rachel India True (born November 15, 1966) is an American film and television actress and former fashion model. She is best known for her roles in such films as The Craft (1996), Nowhere (1997) and Half Baked (1998). True is also known for her role as Mona Thorne on the UPN sitcom Half Half, which ran from 2002-2006.
